export const aboutAuthor = `W. Washika, a dynamic young tele-evangelist, was born on August 12th, 1998, into the nurturing care of Patrick Lukandu and Rosemary Ndeta Mukah, hardworking farmers who instilled in him values of diligence and perseverance. Raised in the tranquil village of Lubinu within the Mumias East Sub-County of Kakamega County, Western Kenya, Washika grew up surrounded by the beauty of nature and the warmth of his community.

From a young age, Washika felt a calling to serve a higher purpose, inspired by the teachings of his faith and the examples of influential figures in the evangelical world. This divine hunger for spiritual enlightenment and a desire to spread the message of God's love became the driving force behind his life's mission.

Washika's educational journey began at Lubinu Primary School, where he laid the foundational pillars of his academic pursuits. He continued his secondary education at St. Joseph's Shibinga, honing his intellectual abilities and expanding his horizons. After completing his secondary education, he pursued further studies at Sang'alo Institute of Science and Technology, where he delved into higher learning.

At the tender age of 25, Washika embarked on a transformative journey, fueled by a vision to ignite a revival across Africa, drawing inspiration from the renowned tele-evangelist Reinhard Bonnke. With a fervent passion for worship and a commitment to touching lives through the power of faith, Washika set out to make a meaningful impact in the lives of those around him.

While nurturing his calling as a tele-evangelist, Washika also pursued his professional career as a dedicated land surveyor in Nairobi City. Balancing the demands of urban life with his spiritual aspirations, Washika found harmony in blending his secular profession with his divine calling, exemplifying a life of service and dedication to both God and community.

Through his first book "Beneath the Crown," Washika shares his remarkable journey of faith, offering insights, reflections, and testimonies that inspire others to seek spiritual fulfillment and pursue their divine calling with unwavering determination. His story serves as a beacon of hope and encouragement, reminding readers of the transformative power of faith and the boundless possibilities that arise when one follows the path illuminated by divine guidance.`;

